  "instructions": [
    "Crack the eggs into a bowl and whisk them together with a fork.",
    "Heat the rapeseed oil in a large non-stick skillet over medium heat.",
    "Pour the egg mixture into the skillet and scramble the eggs until they are cooked through.",
    "Toast the bread slices until they are lightly browned.",
    "Spread a small amount of rapeseed oil on each toast slice.",
    "Place a scrambled egg on top of each toast slice.",
    "Season with salt, black pepper, and garlic powder to taste.",
    "Squeeze a small amount of lime juice over the eggs.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh cilantro.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
